selectSql:
select
	s.id id,
	s.nrparcelas numero_parcelas,
	s.valor valor_servico,
	s.idrubrica id_rubrica,
	s.idservico id_servico,
	case when s.tipo = 'I' then 1 else 2 end as id_servico_cobranca_tipo
from servicorubrica s
insertSql:
insert into ${SCHEMA}.servico_cobranca (
	id,
	numero_parcelas,
	valor_servico,
	id_rubrica,
	id_servico,
	id_servico_cobranca_tipo)
